Are there any regulatory barriers for organic and natural hair dye products?
Yes, regulatory barriers include the need for certification of organic and natural ingredients, compliance with labeling requirements, and adherence to health and safety standards.

What is the consumer perception of organic and natural hair dye products?
Consumers perceive organic and natural hair dye products as safer, healthier, and environmentally friendly compared to synthetic hair dyes.

